<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Bride To Be | FIORE</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <!-- AOS Library CDN -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

   <!-- AOS Library JS -->
   <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
   <script>
     AOS.init({
       duration: 2500,  // Animation lasts for 2500 milliseconds
       delay: 300,      // Delay animation by 300 milliseconds before it starts
       once: true       // Ensures animations run only once (when scrolling down) 
     });
   </script>
 

  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Bride To Be</h1>
      <p>Celebrating Her Journey to “I Do”</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bride-intro" data-aos="fade-up">
    <p>
      The Bride To Be party is more than a celebration—it's a magical gathering of love, laughter, and luxury, crafted especially for the bride's closest circle. From unforgettable moments to heartfelt toasts, every detail is designed to make her feel like royalty before the big day.
    </p>
  </section>
  

  <main class="bride-wrapper">

    <section class="bride-party-section">
        <div class="bride-card" data-aos="fade-left">
          <img src="/img/btb-decor.png" alt="Bride to Be Party Decor">
          <div class="bride-info">
            <h2>Glamorous Decor</h2>
            <p>Set the scene with elegant balloon arches, fairy lights, floral arrangements, and a ‘Bride To Be’ neon sign that glows with glam!</p>
            <a href="/decorators" class="luxury-button">Explore Decorations</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      
        <div class="bride-card" data-aos="fade-right">
          <img src="/img/btb-dress.jpg" alt="Dress Code Ideas">
          <div class="bride-info">
            <h2>Dress Code Themes</h2>
            <p>Go chic with satin robes, pastel dresses, or boho vibes! Let the bride stand out in a custom sash and tiara.</p>
            <a href="/dresses" class="luxury-button">Browse Outfits</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      
        <div class="bride-card" data-aos="fade-left">
          <img src="/img/btb-games.jpg" alt="Fun Party Games">
          <div class="bride-info">
            <h2>Fun Games & Activities</h2>
            <p>Break the ice with games like ‘How Well Do You Know the Bride?’, dares, trivia, and polaroid memory walls.</p>
            <a href="/bride_to_be_games" class="luxury-button">View Games</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      
        <div class="bride-card" data-aos="fade-right">
          <img src="/img/btb-food.png" alt="Party Food & Drinks">
          <div class="bride-info">
            <h2>Elegant Food & Drinks</h2>
            <p>Serve gourmet finger foods, mocktails or champagne towers. Add a dessert table with cupcakes and a bride-themed cake!</p>
            <a href="/catering_services" class="luxury-button">See Catering Ideas</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      
        <div class="bride-card" data-aos="fade-left">
          <img src="/img/btb-photo.jpg" alt="Photo Moments">
          <div class="bride-info">
            <h2>Capturing the Moments</h2>
            <p>Hire a photographer or set up a photo booth to capture every laugh, dance, and sparkle-filled memory of the night.</p>
            <a href="/photographer_collection" class="luxury-button">Book a Photographer</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      
        <div class="bride-card" data-aos="fade-right">
          <img src="/img/btb-gift.png" alt="Gifts & Keepsakes">
          <div class="bride-info">
            <h2>Party Favors & Gifts</h2>
            <p>Send guests home with personalized keepsakes like mini perfumes, candles, or custom thank-you notes from the bride.</p>
            <a href="/GiftShops" class="luxury-button">Browse Gift Ideas</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      
  </main>

</body>
</html>
